-- Mvelaphanda Resources Says Arbitrator Rules Against Khumama Shareholders
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-26T10:41:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-26/mvelaphanda-resources-says-arbitrator-rules-against-khumama-shareholders.html
Mvelaphanda Resources Ltd. said an
arbitrator has decided against a claim brought by former
shareholders of Khumama Platinum Ltd., allowing its unbundling
to continue.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
